com.example.repka_sizebook

Class Profile

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.repka_sizebook.Profile

  • public class Profile
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the main class that is used throughout the program to create profiles, as well as access the profile's variables and set them. For this class, the name of each of the profiles is just the name given when the profile is created.
    Since:
    1.0

      Called when the profile entity is created, which sets the new profile name to the inputted name.
